data.description: Fully Furnished Luxurious two-story, brand new property. Don't miss out on this remarkable 4 bedrooms home. Perfect Airbnb Property or Residential home for first time buyer. This contemporary masterpiece is located in the gated boutique resort of Villa Domani in the heart of everything. Just minutes from the shopping and restaurants at Champions Gate, I4 and 429, and only 15 min to Walt Disney World. Community strategically located in the fast-growing commercial area. Located less than half mile from Reunion. This beautifully home features a modern kitchen, living area, and bedroom with bathroom downstairs. Large sliding doors open to your private courtyard, complete with covered lanai and private heated spa. Upstairs you will find a loft, 2 bedrooms, and oversized master bedroom with bathroom. The community includes a clubhouse which features a fitness center, gathering space, pool and spa. This small private community features only 63 homes, don't miss out on becoming a part of this exclusive property, schedule your showing today!
